Istaraatiijiyadaha tallaalka ee MERS waxaa loo sameeyay iyadoo la adeegsanayo fayrasyo aan la shaqeyn, DNA plasmids, viral vectors, nanoparticles, subunits of virus-like particles and recombinant proteins, qaar kalena waxaa lagu qiimeeyay noocyada xayawaanka.
