Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waqti dheer oo loo baahan yahay horumarinta tallaalka (celcelis ahaan 18 bilood) iyo kala duwanaanshaha dhaqdhaqaaqa ee CoVs ayaa caqabad ku ah in la gudbo.
