Falanqaynta hidde-wadaha ayaa muujisay in coronavirus uu si hidde-wadaag ah ugu jiro kooxda betacoronavirus, subgenus sarbecovirus (genus B) oo leh laba nooc oo ka soo jeeda xayawaanka.
