Angiotensin - converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran dusha sare ee unugyada (cellular membranes) ee sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay isku dheelitirtaa firfircoonaanta enzyme-ka la xiriira ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-converting enzyme' (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa qadarka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadida angiotensin (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa inay u noqoto barta gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Nooca aadanaha ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin - converting enzyme 2 waa zinc - ka kooban metaloenzyme oo ku yaal heerarka hoose iyo dusha sare ee unugyada kale.
borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay N - terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C - terminal colectin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa nooca I ee borotiinka xuubka leh ee leh hal mar oo loo maro oo leh domain aan la beddelay oo enzymatically firfircoon oo ku yaal dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Dhinaca kale, ACE2 waxaa ka go'ay dhinaca kale ee enzyme-ka ee loo yaqaan 'shades' oo ka soo jeeda dhinaca kale ee xuubka, waxaana soo baxaya borotiinka lagu milmi karo ee dhiiga ku soo baxa, ugu dambeynna lagu sii daayaa dhexda ka soo baxa.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa inta badan xubnaha jirka: ACE2 waxay si weyn ugu xirantahay xuubka unugyada nooca II ee sanbabada, unugyada gudaha ee mindhicirka yar, unugyada dhexdhexaadka ah ee wadnaha iyo xididdada iyo unugyada jilicsan ee wadnaha ee xubnaha badankood.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa lagu muujiyaa sidoo kale maskaxda, jirka, hypothalamus iyo lafdhabarta.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay u shaqeyso sidii ACE-da.
ACE waxay u kala jeexdaa hormoonka angiotensin I ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin II'.
ACE2 waxay ka soo saartaa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ka soo saartaa amino acid-ka carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine oo biyo-joojisa si ay u noqoto angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 [des-Arg9] waxay sidoo kale kala jebin kartaa dhowr peptides oo kale oo ay ku jiraan bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphin A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa gaadiidka xuubka ee gaadiidka amino acid ee SLC6A19 waxaana lagu sheegay inay kaalin ka ciyaareyso cudurka wadnaha.
Sida borotiinka xuubka, wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sida barta ugu weyn ee gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayraska corona, oo ay ku jiraan ACE2, HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 waxay isku xiraan borotiinka S1 ee isku xirnaanta ee ACE2 ee unugyada dusha sare ee unugyada, taas oo keentay in ay ku dhacaan endocytosis iyo wareejinta labada fayras iyo enzyme ee unugyada gudaha.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka ayaa sidoo kale u baahan in borotiinka S uu kiciyo nafaqada serine protease TMPRSS2, oo xannibaadeeda ay hadda baaritaan ku jirto daaweyn suurtagal ah. Sababtaas awgeed, qaar ayaa u maleynaya in hoos u dhigista heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka infekshanka.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, hay'ado badan oo xirfadeed iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado daaweynta ACE inhibitor iyo ARB.
Dib u eegis nidaamsan iyo falanqayn meta oo la daabacay 11 July 2012 ayaa lagu ogaaday in "isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay la xiriiraan hoos u dhac weyn oo 34% ah halista sambabada marka loo eego xakamaynta".
Sidoo kale, "Mu'miniinta la daaweeyay ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale la ogaaday inay hoos u dhac ku yimaadeen halista sambabada, kuwaas oo halis sare ugu jira sambabada, gaar ahaan kuwa qaba shuqullada iyo wadnaha oo fashilmay.
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale la xiriira dhimashada dhimashada ee cudurka sambabada, inkastoo natiijooyinka ay ka hooseeyaan halista guud ee sambabada".
Dib-u-habeynta ACE2 ee aadanaha (rhACE2) waxaa loo tixgeliyaa inay tahay daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sanbabada ee daran, waxayna u muuqatay inay hagaajineyso hemodynamics-ka sanbabada iyo nuugista oksijiinta ee dhallaanka doofaarka qaba lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Dadka rhACE2 wuxuu leeyahay nus nolol qiyaastii 10 saacadood iyo bilowga ficilku waa 30 daqiiqo iyadoo leh habka (muddo) saameynta 24 saacadood.
Natiijooyin badan ayaa soo jeedinaya in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daawo rajo leh dadka aan u dulqaadan karin nidaamka xakameynta renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurrada ay ku kordhayaan wareegga angiotensin II. RhACE2 la qasi karo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay tijaabooyinka bukaan socodka ee daaweynta cudurka neefsashada ee daran.
