Ilaa Abriil 2020, dowladda Mareykanka ma la socotid tirakoobka jinsiga ee cudurrada COVID-19.
Cilmi baaris ayaa muujisay in cudurrada fayraska sida Ebola, HIV, Influenza iyo SARS ay si kala duwan u saameeyaan ragga iyo dumarka.
Tiro badan oo ka mid ah shaqaalaha caafimaadka, gaar ahaan kalkaalisada caafimaadka, waa haween, waxayna u badan tahay inay la kulmaan fayraska.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku dhawaaqay 11 Febraayo 2020 in magaca rasmiga ah ee cudurka uu noqon doono "COVID-19".
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, madaxa WHO, ayaa sheegay in CO ay ka dhigan tahay Corona, VI ay ka dhigan tahay Virus, D ay ka dhigan tahay Cudur, iyo 19 ay ka dhigan tahay sanadkii uu cudurku markii ugu horreysay la aqoonsaday, 31 December 2019.
Magaca waxaa loo doortay in laga fogaado tixraacyada goobta juqraafiyeed ee gaarka ah (sida Shiinaha), noocyada xayawaanka ama kooxda dadka, taas oo waafaqsan talooyinka caalamiga ah ee loogu talagalay magacaabista ujeedada looga hortago in lagu ceebeeyo. Fayraska keena COVID-19 waxaa loo yaqaan 'Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2' (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO waxay kaloo isticmaashaa "virus-ka COVID-19" iyo "virus-ka mas'uulka ka ah COVID-19" ee isgaarsiinta dadweynaha.
Cudurada iyo fayrasyada labadaba waxaa loo yaqaan "Covid-19".
Intii uu socday faafitaanka bilowga ah ee Wuhan, Shiinaha, fayraska iyo cudurka waxaa loo yaqaan "coronavirus" iyo "Wuhan coronavirus".
Bishii Janaayo 2020, WHO waxay ku talisay 2019-nCov iyo 2019-nCoV inay yihiin magacyada ku meel gaarka ah ee fayraska iyo cudurka cudurka neefta ee daran, taas oo u hoggaansamaysa tilmaamaha 2015 ee ah in aan la isticmaalin meelaha ka baxsan ee cudurka iyo magacyada fayraska.
Magacyada rasmiga ah ee COVID-19 iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la sii daayay 11 Febraayo 2020.
Sababtoo ah xadka awoodda ee silsiladaha sahayda caadiga ah, qaar ka mid ah soo saarayaasha dhijitaalka ah ayaa daabacaya qalabka caafimaadka sida naasaha iyo qaybaha ventilator.
Tusaale ahaan, markii isbitaal Talyaani ah uu si deg deg ah u baahday waalka hawo-mareenka, oo alaab-qeybiyaha uusan awoodin inuu ku bixiyo waqtiga loo baahan yahay, shirkad bilow ah oo maxalli ah ayaa dib u-injineer ku sameysay 100 waalka loo baahan yahay habeenkii.
Ka dib markii uu dillaacay COVID-19, shirqool, macluumaad khaldan iyo macluumaad khaldan oo ku saabsan asalka, heerka, ka hortagga, daaweynta iyo dhinacyada kale ee cudurka ayaa soo ifbaxay oo si dhakhso leh ugu faafay internetka.
Dadku waxay u muuqdaan inay awood u leeyihiin inay fayras ku faafiyaan xayawaanka kale.
Daraasaddu waxay ku fashilantay in ay hesho caddeyn ku saabsan nuqulka fayraska ee doofaarka, ducks, iyo digaagga.
Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal la ansixiyay oo lagu daaweyn karo cudurka.
Cilmi baarista caalamiga ah ee tallaallada iyo dawooyinka COVID-19 waxaa sameeya ururada dowladda, kooxaha tacliinta iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha.
Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa bilaabay "Tijaabooyin Midnimo" si loo qiimeeyo saameynta daaweynta ee afar ka mid ah xeryahooda jira ee ka hortagga fayraska ee leh rajada ugu badan ee waxtarka.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah ma jiro tallaal la heli karo, laakiin hay'ado kala duwan ayaa si firfircoon u horumarinaya murashaxiinta tallaalka.
Shaqada hore ee SARS-CoV ayaa la adeegsanayaa sababtoo ah SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 labaduba waxay isticmaalaan ACE2 receptor si ay u galaan unugyada aadanaha.
Saddex istaraatijiyad oo tallaal ah ayaa la tijaabiyaa.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay higsanayaan inay sameeyaan tallaal fayras oo dhamaystiran.
Isticmaalka fayrasyada noocaas ah, ha ahaadeen kuwo aan shaqeyn ama kuwa dhintay, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu kiciyo jawaab celin dhaqso ah oo difaaca jirka ee jirka bini'aadamka ee cudurka cusub ee COVID-19.
Istaraatiijiyad kale, tallaalka subunit, ayaa ujeedkeedu yahay in la sameeyo tallaal ka dhigaya nidaamka difaaca jirka mid u nugul qaybaha qaar ee fayraska.
Marka la eego SARS-CoV-2, cilmi baarista noocan oo kale ah waxay diiradda saartaa borotiinka S-contact kaas oo ka caawiya fayraska inuu galo ACE2 enzyme receptor.
istaraatijiyad saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA tallaal, farsamo cusub oo lagu sameeyo tallaalka).
Talaalada tijaabada ah ee mid ka mid ah istaraatijiyaddan waa in la tijaabiyaa badbaadada iyo waxtarka. 16-kii Maarso 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka ayaa ka bilaabatay Seattle oo ay ku jiraan afar mutadawiciin.
Tallaalku wuxuu ka kooban yahay koodh aan waxyeello lahayn oo hidde ah oo laga soo guuriyay fayraska keena cudurka. Kororka ku tiirsan antibody-ka ayaa lagu tilmaamay caqabad suurtagal ah horumarinta tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin waa mid muran badan.
In ka badan 300 oo tijaabooyin caafimaad oo firfircoon ayaa la wadaa ilaa Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa qiimeynayay daaweynta horey loo oggolaaday ee duumada, oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Iyada oo sagaal tijaabo oo wajiga III ah oo ku saabsan Remdesivir ay ku jiraan dalal badan, inta badan cilmi baarista Shiinaha ayaa lagu shaqeynayaa daawooyinka anti-viral ee dib loo isticmaali karo, oo la filayo in la soo bandhigo dhammaadka Abriil.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, dib u eegis firfircoon oo ku saabsan horumarka bukaan socodka ee tallaallada COVID-19 iyo murashaxiinta dawooyinka ayaa socda. Daawooyin badan oo jira oo ka hortag ah COVID-19 ayaa la qiimeynayaa, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo ay weheliso interferon beta.
Ilaa Maarso 2020, waxaa jira caddayn tijaabo ah oo ku saabsan waxtarka Remdesivir.
Bukaannada lagu daaweeyey isticmaalka aan la oggolayn ee remdesivir ayaa la arkay horumar caafimaad.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee wajiga III waxaa lagu wadaa Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine oo horey loogu isticmaali jiray daaweynta duumada ayaa lagu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020 iyadoo natiijooyin bilow ah la helay.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa la codsaday in cilmi baarista dib loo eego.
Hay'adaha caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa ku talinaya in la isticmaalo chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, Machadka Wuhan ee Fayroska ayaa ku talinaya qiyaasta maalinlaha ah ee hal garaam, isagoo xusay in laba jeer qiyaastaas ay tahay mid aad khatar u ah oo dhimasho u horseedi karta.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay oggolaansho degdeg ah oo loogu talagalay hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine, iyadoo ay ku saleysan tahay garashada dhakhaatiirta daaweynta dadka qaba COVID-19. Tilmaamaha daabacaadda 7aad ee Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ku jira interferon, ribavirin ama umiphenovir oo loo isticmaalo ilaalinta COVID-19.
Xogta hordhaca ah waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso sare oo ribabirin ah loo baahan yahay xakameynta SARS-CoV-2 ee macmalka ah.
Nitasoxanide waxaa lagu talinayaa in si dheeraad ah loogu barto xayawaanka ka dib markii la muujiyey hoos u dhaca heerarka hoose ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasadaha ayaa muujiyay in horudhaca borotiinka xiriirka ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ' uu muhiim u yahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka qaataha ACE2.
Daraasadaha loo sameeyay chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo leh ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaadyo waaweyn oo ka hortagay bulshada caafimaadka inay qaataan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasad dheeraad ah. Oseltamivir ma xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 ee macmalka ah ee hareeraha ah mana laha door la yaqaan daaweynta COVID-19.
Kordhinta heerarka cytokines waxay noqon kartaa dhibaato marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyin ka hortagga kororka tirada cytokines. Toqulizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib markii la dhammeystiray daraasad yar.
Waxaa lagu wadaa tijaabo heer qaran ah oo wajiga 2 ah oo aan la isku dayin Talyaaniga kadib markii ay natiijooyin togan ka muujiyeen dadka qaba cudurrada daran.
Marka la eego baaritaanka dhiigga ee serum ferritin si loo aqoonsado kororka heerarka cytokines, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu hortago kororka noocan oo kale ah, oo loo maleynayo inuu sababay dhimashada dadka qaar ee la taaban karo.
Interleukin-6 inhibitor waxaa FDA-da loo oggolaaday 2017 si loogu daaweeyo cudurka loo yaqaan 'cytokine release syndrome' ee steroids-ka ee loo yaqaan 'carotenoid refractory cytokine release syndrome' oo ay sabab u tahay sabab kale, CAR T cell therapy.
Ilaa maanta ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo la isku xiray oo la xakameeyay oo muujinaya in tosalizuumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
U wareejinta difaaca dabiiciga ah iyo kan xooggan ee ay soo saarto nidaamka difaaca ee dadka ka bogsada COVID-19 dadka u baahan, ayaa loo baaray sidii hab aan tallaal ahayn oo tallaal aan la qabin.
Talooyinkan waxaa loo adeegsaday SARS iyadoo natiijooyin aan la hubin.
Xasaasiyadda fayraska waa habka la filayo ee daaweynta antibody ee aan la shaqeyn karin ay dhexdhexaadin karto difaaca SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale oo waxqabadka ah, sida antibody - ku tiirsan cytotoxicity unugyada iyo / ama phagocytosis waa suuragal.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibody-ka ee aan shaqeyn, tusaale ahaan isticmaalka monoclonal immunity-ka la sameeyay, ayaa horumarinta lagu jiro.
Wax soo saarka serum-ka caafimaadka faa'iidada leh, oo ka kooban qayb dareere ah oo ka mid ah dhiigga bukaannada soo kabsaday oo leh difaaca gaarka ah ee fayraska, ayaa loo kordhin karaa si loo qorsheeyo si dhakhso leh.
Cudurka Coronavirus, waa koox ka mid ah cudurada la xiriira isqabqabsiga
Lee Wenliang, oo ah dhakhtar ka tirsan Isbitaalka Dhexe ee Wuhan, ayaa ku dhacay COVID-19 kadib markii uu kor u qaaday wacyiga faafitaanka fayraska, wuxuuna dhintay.
